---
source: src/cli/app.rs
expression: "command_help_for_test(\"doctor\")"
---
Show config paths, executable/helper availability, and safety mode

Usage: doctor [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --mode <MODE>
          Safety mode to inspect (default: balanced): plan, ask, edit, or auto
          
          [default: default]

      --install-missing
          Install missing OpenCode 2, tokei, and ctags with global mise config

      --install-sighthound
          Source-build pinned Sighthound with Rust 1.96 and global mise config

      --check
          Validate effective OpenCode agents, commands, MCP, and models; exit nonzero on failure

  -h, --help
          Print help
